'From Squeak2.8alpha of 13 January 2000 [latest update: #2164] on 17 May 2000 at 5:56:51 pm'!"Change Set:		dndTransition-swDate:			17 May 2000Author:			Scott WallaceRepairs existing instances of PasteUpMorph and its subclasses so their openness-to-drag-and-drop in the new regime is the same as it was in the old."!!PasteUpMorph methodsFor: 'dropping/grabbing' stamp: 'sw 5/17/2000 17:48'!convertToNewDragNDrop	openToDragNDrop ifNotNil:		[self enableDragNDrop: openToDragNDrop.		openToDragNDrop _ nil]! !"Postscript:"PasteUpMorph allSubInstances do: [:anInst | anInst convertToNewDragNDrop].!